articles.description: Miye Oni scored 19 points with six rebounds and six assists and Yale defeated Cornell 74-65 on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Oni leads Yale to 74-65 win over Cornell

articles.description: Ahmad Caver had 17 points, 10 assists and six steals as Old Dominion rolled to an 82-69 victory over Louisiana Tech on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Old Dominion cruises in 82-69 win over Louisiana Tech

articles.description: Eddie Reese scored 19 points with six assists and Southern beat Arkansas-Pine Bluff 70-62 on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Reese with 19, Southern beats Arkansas-Pine Bluff 70-62

articles.description: Cortez Edwards scored 12 points, grabbed 10 rebounds, distributed six assists and had five steals and Southern Mississippi cruised to 72-54 win over Charlotte on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Edwards leads Southern Mississippi past Charlotte 72-54

articles.description: The No. 2 Cavaliers force overtime with a pair of late buckets from Ty Jerome, but in the extra session, the Hokies' Kerry Blackshear Jr. scores an and-1 with under 10 seconds remaining for a 61-60 victory.
articles.headline: Virginia Tech takes down No. 2 Virginia in OT
